                  </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="walk-thru-step">
            <div class="content-wrapper">
                <img id='shrink-me' class="lazyload" data-src=<%= "#{ENV['CDN_URL']}/images/tools/lessons/lessons_intro_slide_2.png" %> alt="lessons image" style="max-height:266px">
